participants.name: DAVID COGAN
participants.title: Entrepreneur, Radio Host (AM/FM), Mentor, Founder Eliances "Where Entrepreneurs Align"

messages.message:
Thanks for reaching out. You need to check out what we, Eliances.com are doing. I'd like to invite you to a private ROUNDtable of 60 leaders which meets every Tuesday at 8:30am for a couple hours at our sponsor ASU SkySong. I promise you an experience you won't forget. 

We reach maximum capacity at every event, so please let me know which Tuesday will work. You can check out our press release on ASU website https://skysong.asu.edu/press-releases/eliances-roundtable-and-asu-skysong-join-forces-create-entrepreneur-forum-arizona

And go to http://www.eliances.com/public/Testimonials.cfm to see who has been part of our community. 

Which Tuesday works?
Thanks,
David
I still have a boss so I'll ha e to tell them ahead of the so hopefully next week.
I've been to skysong before with the last startup I worked on. That is a sweet setup you guys have!
Let me know your email address as I will need to get you the formal invite to register for next week . Thanks.
Great, just emailed you the private invite for next week to register. Thanks, David
